Packagist

     * [https://github.com/hirak/packagist-crawler]Packagist-Crawler -
       Script to mirror Packagist metadata.

Packagist Mirrors

     * North America
          + Canada - [https://packagist.org/]packagist.org
     * South America
          + Brazil - [https://packagist.com.br/]packagist.com.br
     * Asia
          + Japan - [https://packagist.jp/]packagist.jp
          + China -
            [https://pkg.phpcomposer.com/]packagist.phpcomposer.com

Composer Repositories

Private Packagist

     * [https://packagist.com/]Private Packagist Cloud - A Composer
       Repository as a Service for private packages and to mirror packages
       from other repositories
     * [https://packagist.com/]Private Packagist Enterprise - On-premise
       self-hosted version of Private Packagist

Satis

     * [https://github.com/wemakecustom/gitlab-composer]Gitlab-Composer -
       This is a branch/tag indexer for Gitlab repositories.
     * [https://github.com/ludofleury/satisfy]Satisfy - Satis composer
       repository manager with a Web UI.
     * [https://github.com/realshadow/satis-control-panel]Satis Control
       Panel - A simple web UI for managing your Satis Repository with
       optional CI integration.
     * [https://github.com/benschw/satis-go]Satis Go - A web server for
       managing Satis configuration and hosting the generated Composer
       repository.

Toran Proxy

     * [https://toranproxy.com/]ToranProxy (deprecated) - In addition to
       providing a composer repository ToranProxy acts as a proxy server
       for Packagist and GitHub.
